{"type":"message","id":"f8e0e599","parentId":"690394a7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:27:34.696Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gg233hdopo7s_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4329\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=982\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] and\r\n[mutation proposed] and\r\n[master 3496ffc] pulse: 2026-03-24 152714\n 6 files changed, 197 insertions(+), 61 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152714.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152714.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 152613.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152714 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified the Constant Format Problem - tokens with freq=160, CFI=1.00 are metaprogramming artifacts, not causal content. The proposed solution is hybrid scoring: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). This experiment validates whether this formula distinguishes \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\".\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"glow-wharf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4329\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=982\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] and\r\n[mutation proposed] and\r\n[master 3496ffc] pulse: 2026-03-24 152714\n 6 files changed, 197 insertions(+), 61 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152714.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152714.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 152613.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152714 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified the Constant Format Problem - tokens with freq=160, CFI=1.00 are metaprogramming artifacts, not causal content. The proposed solution is hybrid scoring: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). This experiment validates whether this formula distinguishes \"constant fo